blog.description:
Random blog. 

Eliot | 24 | she/her | 🇮🇹🇬🇧🇩🇪 | Scorpio | Fanwriter | Prompt Provider | K-popper

✨anime&manga✨Tokio Hotel✨Haikyuu✨BTS✨EXO✨

body:
Fic Game: Kiss Version

There was a fic game with so many kiss prompts some time ago and I already filled some of them on Facebook in my mother language (Italian), but I want to complete the whole list, just to feel satisfied with myself. Will you help me? ;)

Ask me and choose a kiss prompt and a pairing and I will write a mini-fic in the answer! The bold prompts are already done, so please try to choose other free prompts first.

4. Awkward kiss

6. “I’m sorry” kiss

8. Seductive kiss

9. “War’s End” kiss

11. “I almost lost you” kiss

12. Kiss on the nose

13. Kiss on the ear

14. Kiss on the neck

15. Kiss on the back

16. New Year’s kiss

17. Needing to kiss to hide from bad guys

19. Shy kiss

20. Surprised kiss

21. Kiss on a dare

22. Top Of Head Kisses

24. Kiss of life

27. Giggly kiss

28. First kiss

30. Kiss under a full moon

31. Kisses Where One Person Is Sitting In The Other’s Lap

32. Kiss at dawn

33. Kiss in a dream

35. When One Person’s Face Is Scrunched Up, And The Other One Kisses Their Lips/Nose/Forehead

36. Height Difference Kisses Where One Person Has To Bend Do Wn And The Other Is On Their Tippy Toes

37. It’s-the-end-of-the-world kiss

38. Awkward teenage crush kiss

39. Starting With A Kiss Meant To Be Gentle, Ending Up In Passion

40. Hiding/hoping not to be caught kiss

41. Soft kiss

42. Staring At The Other’s Lips, Trying Not To Kiss Them, Before Giving In

44. Following The Kiss With A Series Of Kisses Down The Neck

45. Passionate kiss

46. Long kiss

47. Quick kiss

48. Being Unable To Open Their Eyes For A Few Moments Afterward

49. One Small Kiss, Pulling Away For An Instant, Then Devouring Each Other

50. Routine Kisses Where The Other Person Presents Their Cheek/Forehead For The Hello/Goodbye Kiss Without Even Looking Up From What They’re Doing

51. Public kiss

52. Accidentally Witnessed kiss

54. Lazy Morning Kisses Before They’ve Even Opened Their Eyes, Still Mumbling Half-Incoherently, Not Wanting To Wake Up 55. True Love kiss

56. Breaking The Kiss To Say Something, Staying So Close That You’re Murmuring Into Each Other’s Mouths

58. Throwing Their Arms Around The Other Person, Holding Them Close While They Kiss

60. [bonus choice]

I know that the numbers are not rights, but it’s just for me to keep them separated from the prompts I already did in the past. I tagged some ships for visibility, but if a fandom is mentioned then you can ask any pairing belonging to that fandom without problems. Go!
